 treba Signal, nebo Threema ?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Ahoj, slo by prosim pro CZ komunitu mit neco lepsiho, nez Telegram ? Idealne neco decentralizovaneho (Matrix/Elemet, Session) a kdyz uz ne decentralizovane, tak bezpecnejsi, nez je Telegram, treba Signal, nebo Threema ?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1460269693305749668", "author": "recrof", "author_handle": "recrof", "user_id": "205303085910720514", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/205303085910720514/8ccde84f87c6a23fe1212f4c9a64a4b8.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, January 12, 2026 8:50 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-12 8:50 a.m.", "text": "podla mna problem telegramu nekonci len pri bezpecnosti je to dost retardovana platforma pre komunity vo vseobecnosti.. to uz aj discord je pouzitelnejsi", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>podla mna problem telegramu nekonci len pri bezpecnosti <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"🙂\"\n    title=\"slight_smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f642.svg\"> je to dost retardovana platforma pre komunity vo vseobecnosti.. to uz aj discord je pouzitelnejsi</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>6</span></div><div class=chatlog__reaction title=point_up><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=☝️ src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/261d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>2</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1461841024921112789", "author": "Downet", "author_handle": "downet", "user_id": "558384229717770285", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/558384229717770285/385eda5f7ea710268317991f8108d7e4.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, January 16, 2026 4:54 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-16 4:54 p.m.", "text": "Nejlepsi by bylo udelat asi stare dobre forum nicmene nemyslim si, ze lidi premluvime switchnout jinam. (bohuzel, telegram taky moc nemusim)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Nejlepsi by bylo udelat asi stare dobre forum <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😄\"\n    title=\"smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f604.svg\"> nicmene nemyslim si, ze lidi premluvime switchnout jinam. <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"🙁\"\n    title=\"slight_frown\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f641.svg\"> (bohuzel, telegram taky moc nemusim)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1461843432317390922", "author": "Downet", "author_handle": "downet", "user_id": "558384229717770285", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/558384229717770285/385eda5f7ea710268317991f8108d7e4.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, January 16, 2026 5:03 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-16 5:03 p.m.", "text": "MeshCore v CZ mění preset! (Od ledna 2026) Frequency= 869,432 MHz Bandwidth = 62.5 kHz SF = 7 CR = 5 V aplikaci jako Czech Republic (Narrow).", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>MeshCore v CZ měn&#237; preset! (Od ledna 2026)\n\nFrequency= 869,432 MHz\n\nBandwidth = 62.5 kHz\n\nSF = 7\n\nCR = 5\n\nV aplikaci jako Czech Republic (Narrow).</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=face_with_raised_eyebrow><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🤨 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f928.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1462063214039793908", "author": "𝔇𝔬𝔫𝔞𝔩𝔡", "author_handle": "donaldinos", "user_id": "809534029979844708", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/809534029979844708/4a522130edf916ceaa87231b736c58f4.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, January 17, 2026 7:37 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-17 7:37 a.m.", "text": "Zdravim, netusi niekdo, jestli Meshcore umoznuje nejak definovat nektery GPIO pin jako user button abych ho mohl pouzit jako Wake-up tlacitko na sve RAK19003 desce ?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Zdravim, netusi niekdo, jestli Meshcore umoznuje nejak definovat nektery GPIO pin jako user button abych ho mohl pouzit jako Wake-up tlacitko na sve RAK19003 desce ?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1462063900014149642", "author": "𝔇𝔬𝔫𝔞𝔩𝔡", "author_handle": "donaldinos", "user_id": "809534029979844708", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/809534029979844708/4a522130edf916ceaa87231b736c58f4.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, January 17, 2026 7:39 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-17 7:39 a.m.", "text": "Nemusi se hned nutne cela komunita switchovat, stacilo by na zacatek jeste povolit a nejak aspon podporovat/sledovat i jiny interaktivni kanal, nez jenom Telegram. Ja chapu, ze to muze vest ke tristeni komunity ale takhle zase prichazi komunita o mozne dalsi aktivne cleny, jen proto, ze nepodporuji Telegram. Mozna by to stalo za zamysleni. Klidne by za mne mohla zustat jako druha moznost Discord, nemam s tim problem.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Nemusi se hned nutne cela komunita switchovat, stacilo by na zacatek jeste povolit a nejak aspon podporovat/sledovat i jiny interaktivni kanal, nez jenom Telegram. Ja chapu, ze to muze vest ke tristeni komunity ale takhle zase prichazi komunita o mozne dalsi aktivne cleny, jen proto, ze nepodporuji Telegram. Mozna by to stalo za zamysleni. Klidne by za mne mohla zustat jako druha moznost Discord, nemam s tim problem.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/558384229717770285/385eda5f7ea710268317991f8108d7e4.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=downet>Downet</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1461843432317390922')\"> MeshCore v CZ měn&#237; preset! (Od ledna 2026)\n\nFrequency= 869,432 MHz\n\nBandwidth = 62.5 kHz\n\nSF = 7\n\nCR = 5\n\nV aplikaci jako Czech Republic (Narrow). </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1462109440584192097", "author": "Downet", "author_handle": "downet", "user_id": "558384229717770285", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/558384229717770285/385eda5f7ea710268317991f8108d7e4.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, January 17, 2026 10:40 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-17 10:40 a.m.", "text": "@Honza co se ti nezda?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"honza_87628\">@Honza</span> co se ti nezda? <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😄\"\n    title=\"smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f604.svg\"></span></d